<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoenix">Phoenix</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>等众多音乐人都进行了表演，关于谁可能成为主角的谣言就开始流传。 2024年。</p><p>到目前为止，猜测范围包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">Harry Styles</a> 。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-headliners-2024-rumours-bookies-3458989">在这里找到<em>《NME</em> 》传闻演员的完整名单</a>。</p><p>在 2023 年这一标志性音乐节中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-2023-liveblog-sunday-news-reviews-rumours-pictures-3460915">亮点包括</a>John 跨越职业生涯的告别表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/elton-john-glastonbury-2023-review-setlist-photos-3461062">NME 称其为“音乐节有史以来最好的头条节目之一”，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>的惊喜节目最终揭开了神秘乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/foo-fighters-play-pyramid-stage-as-mystery-band-the-churnups-revealed-3460119">The Churnups</a>的身份以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cate-blanchett-dance-on-stage-with-sparks-at-glastonbury-festival-3460441">凯特·布兰切特 (Cate Blanchett) 与 Sparks 的舞台舞蹈表演</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-ticket-sale-date-seemingly-confirmed-by-emily-eavis-3502887">艾米莉·伊维斯 (Emily Eavis) 似乎确认了格拉斯顿伯里音乐节后的售票日期，</a>该日期首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 1975 年使用假马蒂·希利政治广告宣传巡演https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-promote-tour-using-fake-matty-healy-political-ad-3502877?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-1975-promote-tour-使用假马蒂希利政治广告Emma WilkesSat, 23 Sep 2023 10:04:55 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3502877 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马蒂·希利" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>视频中希利发表了关于救赎的演讲</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-promote-tour-using-fake-matty-healy-political-ad-3502877">使用假马蒂·希利政治广告《1975 年宣传巡演》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马蒂·希利" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-scott-legato-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975 乐队</a>正在宣传他们的“Still…At Their Very Best”巡演，并播放了一段由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">Matty Healy</a>主演的模仿美国政治广告的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-1975-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3464005">1975 年伦敦现场演出：网络狂热中的庆祝活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>视频显示希利扮演一名政客，参观施粥处、与执法部门交谈并前往建筑工地。</p><p> “在美国的心脏地带，我们知道救赎不仅仅是一个词，”希利在戏剧性的空中镜头中说道。</p><p> “这是我们对自己和彼此做出的承诺。我们国家的故事是第二次机会，即使面对错误也能开辟一条前进的道路。</p><p> “这是关于重建破碎的地方，治愈受伤的地方，并齐心协力创造比以前更强大的东西。</p><p> “但救赎不仅仅是一个抽象的想法。这是我们每天在社区中看到的事情。这是单亲父母做两份工作来养活孩子。在服务他人中找到目标的退伍军人。还有在困难时伸出援手的邻居。</p><p> “作为一个国家，我们必须在我们的政策和行动中拥抱救赎。我们必须改革我们的刑事司法体系，将重点放在康复上，而不仅仅是惩罚上。我们必须确保每个美国人都能获得优质教育和负担得起的医疗保健，以便每个人而不是少数人都能获得救赎的机会。</p><p> “一起。我们可以建设一个没有人被过去所定义、每个人都有机会做出贡献、并且同情心是进步之道的未来。</p><p> “我相信在美国，救赎不仅仅是一个遥远的梦想。这是我们每天携手创造的现实。</p><p> “加入我们，迈向更美好的明天。我们可以书写美国历史的新篇章。一起，在这里，参加‘仍然……处于最佳状态’巡演。”</p><p>检查下面的剪辑： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CxgJWnXxm1d/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px